   Technology:
   Daisy Systems Says
   Bondholders Seek
   Bankruptcy Status
</HL>
<DATE>
06/04/90
</DATE>
<SO>
WALL STREET JOURNAL (J), PAGE B4
</SO>
<CO>
   DAZXC
